HEADWORD: Oxime
<hw>Ox"ime</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>One
of a series of isonitroso derivatives obtained by the action of
hydroxylamine on aldehydes or ketones.</def>⟦br⟧
